headline: Larson Named Lowe’s Vendor of Year, Millwork
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., October 23, 2025--Larson, the leading storm door brand in North America and part of Fortune Brands Innovations, Inc. (NYSE: FBIN or "Fortune Brands"), was recently named by Lowe’s as the 2025 Vendor of the Year, Millwork division. Larson was recognized for its commitment to quality, innovation, value, and customer service, including innovative product launches and strategic investments in customer experience.
